### Authentication and Setup

- Configure API keys and project IDs
- Implement proper credential management
- Handle authentication errors gracefully

### Session Lifecycle

- Create and manage browser sessions
- Implement session pooling and reuse
- Handle session cleanup and resource management
- Monitor session health and performance

### Error Handling

- Implement comprehensive error handling
- Use StepResult pattern for all SDK operations
- Log errors with appropriate context
- Provide fallback strategies for failures

### Integration Patterns

- Wrap SDK calls in service classes
- Implement retry logic with exponential backoff
- Use dependency injection for testability
- Follow tenant-aware design principles
